subproject.description:
" Democratic governance issues i.e. accountability, transparency, integrity, gender responsive initiatives addresses in context of Organization of Eastern Caribbean States Development Charter and MDG".
a) Amendments to Constitution and legislative instruments drafted to support constitutional and public sector reform initiatives;
b)Regional Policies and Strategies approved to strengthen Organizations of Eastern Caribbean States (OECS) European Union and implemented at the national level;
c)Establishment of an institutionalised system of mult-stakeholder dialogue to strengthen national decision-making processes with greater participation of Civil Society Organizations;
d) Regional collaboration deepened by increased civil society and community participation, supported by enhanced national-level Information and Communications Technology, Sports and Culture programmes; and 
e) Ensuring gender equality in the above outcomes;
